    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深夜街市，等待你不打烊</h2>在深夜街市经营一家不打烊的餐厅，从炸串店到居酒屋，餐厅品类任你挑选！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761190/extras/1a1e0cb5d0b73bc38f9889a753fcb7d3.avif?t=1762830082\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我的小馆，打造最强店铺</h2>通过持续经营不断挣钱，然后升级自己的餐厅，藉此获得更多食材和菜品，让生意蒸蒸日上！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761190/extras/bbcad038d7dd0f87e26bed44409fdcc9.avif?t=1762830082\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >美味料理，挑战好评极限</h2>在限定时间内，尽可能招待更多食客，根据他们的要求，准确筹备料理，然后端盘上菜！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761190/extras/53a06179c97e34b64823c1e52071787f.avif?t=1762830082\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富玩法，尽享店主乐趣</h2>通过搭配不同食材创造出新的菜品，享受身为店主自给自足的满足感和成就感，更多玩法，等你去发现！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761190/extras/19800431f0ff3ab2800dd4d85500c608.avif?t=1762830082\" width=616 height=346 /></span>",
